    "description": "<strong>UNDERTUNNEL</strong>, the latest creation from <i>Screaming Void</i>, is a story driven sci-fi FPS with RPG elements. It will take you on an irreverent twisting journey through the sprawling NEO-INDUSTRIAL tunnels beneath a dystopian metropolis. YOU must make your way down and through... <br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183220/extras/8440799e79f1cd4bf4727c74e854d233.avif?t=1762994608\" width=400 height=68 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Explore the subterranean tunnels and <strong>SEARCH</strong> for clues and useful items<br></li><li>Question its strange inhabitants for the answers you seek</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183220/extras/3e1466d76ab60a04451364d949189798.avif?t=1762994608\" width=400 height=68 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Reconfigure computer systems and security devices<br></li><li><strong>HACK</strong> terminals and tunnel droids</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183220/extras/14f7bd27c4daab454364b818cefc9a8c.avif?t=1762994608\" width=400 height=68 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Navigate traps and <strong>JUMP</strong> deathly drops<br></li><li>Balance on pipes and descend disused maintenance shafts</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183220/extras/86fefd68386259223a37d84654a55b98.avif?t=1762994608\" width=400 height=68 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Engage in hard-hitting combat with violent gangs<br></li><li>Learn to survive as you <strong>FIGHT</strong> terrible mutants and unspeakable horrors</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183220/extras/019c693c712f5012e1e6a0ae363f848c.avif?t=1762994608\" width=400 height=68 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Try not to <strong>PUKE</strong> from the smells, sights and sounds of... UNDERTUNNEL</li></ul>",
